text.data-name: Luggage is delivered contactless with documents exchanged digit

g.text: Luggage is delivered contactless with documents exchanged digitally. Deliveries will be made only in green zones. Baggage with 1st shield of packing will be delivered at doorstep

text.data-name: Each bag is packed 2 times (2 shield packing) to ensure lesser

g.text: Each bag is packed 2 times (2 shield packing) to ensure lesser exposure after sanitization. SMS is sent after order is picked up

text.data-name: Price and Proceed will be activated only on selection of terms

g.text: Price and Proceed will be activated only on selection of terms and conditions Complete address will be taken pre dispatch. Pin code cannot be changed after confirmation. SMS and Email will be sent on Order Confirmation

text.data-name: Proceed to baggage carousel with documents ready with Order# Ca

g.text: Proceed to baggage carousel with documents ready with Order# CarterX personnel name and number will be sent via SMS. Meet of CarterX personnel is MANDATORY

text.data-name: Passenger proceeds to OLA to board cab on PRIORITY and interact

g.text: Passenger proceeds to OLA to board cab on PRIORITY and interact with CarterX to confirm the bag

text.data-name: Slot based delivery service. Vehicle tracking SMS will be sent

g.text: Slot based delivery service. Vehicle tracking SMS will be sent at the time of dispatch
